{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c454582f-92e6-4f1e-bb24-5b286dbd3112","content":"Override `CreateWindow` in your `App.xaml.cs` and subscribe to each event on the window:\n\n```csharp\nprotected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n{\n    var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n    window.Created    += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Created\");\n    window.Activated  += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Activated\");\n    window.Deactivated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Deactivated\");\n    window.Stopped    += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Stopped\");\n    window.Resumed    += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Resumed\");\n    window.Destroying += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Destroying\");\n\n    // iOS / Mac Catalyst only\n    window.Backgrounding += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Backgrounding\");\n\n    return window;\n}\n```\n\n**Typical sequence:**\n\n| Action | Events fired |\n|---|---|\n| App launch | `Created` → `Activated` |\n| User switches away | `Deactivated` → `Stopped` (→ `Backgrounding` on iOS) |\n| User returns | `Resumed` → `Activated` |\n| App closed | `Deactivated` → `Stopped` → `Destroying` |\n\nReplace `Debug.WriteLine` with your preferred logger (e.g., `ILogger`, `Console.WriteLine`, or a file logger) as needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"93d7b821-56d9-43b2-9e7f-a2b84e731d14","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about .NET MAUI Window lifecycle events and how to subscribe to them for debugging/logging purposes. This is a general programming knowledge question - I don't need to search the codebase for this.\n\nLet me provide a concise answer about MAUI Window lifecycle events.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the Window class exposes these lifecycle events:\n- Created\n- Activated\n- Deactivated\n- Stopped\n- Resumed\n- Destroying\n- Backgrounding (iOS/Mac Catalyst)\n\nYou can override `CreateWindow` in your `App` class or subscribe to them on the Window object.","outputTokens":522,"requestId":"DBC2:17C00:A5D55:CEF0D:69F54AEC"},"id":"8db1b0ce-5709-4991-93db-3e5ebb6d1e4c","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:53:09.889Z","parentId":"63816314-345c-4a7f-85d9-80a472f142b0"}
